<p>Nag Champa Rose Soap can be used as a skin toner, cleanser and moisturiser and the infusion of Rose petals gives coolness, freshness and can have a lovely calming effect. This bar contains Palm Oil which is rich in vitamin A, E and fatty acids with Coconut Oil which acts as a protective antioxidant and keeps the skin soft and smooth, preventing premature ageing and wrinkling and Glycerine which draws moisture from the air and holds it to the skin. For best results, lather in with your hands and apply full on the body for at least two or three minutes and rinse well to realize the properties. This soap is pH balanced &amp; allergy tested and is also free from animal fat. 75g bar.</p>